Class HashNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • assignment.HashNode

  • public class HashNode
extends java.lang.Object
    LinkedList-type structure for hashing Tic-Tac-Toe (TTT) boards. This Object is For handling hash collisions via chaining.
    Author:
    Matthew "crickon" Grillo
